    "description": {
      "value": "<h2></b>Description</b></h2></p><p>This glowing violet liquid is ice-cold regardless of the surrounding temperature. This elixir allows a character to bypass the cold immunity or cold resistance of creatures she attacks with her magic. For 6 rounds after drinking a truefrost elixir, a character's spells, spell-like abilities, and supernatural abilities that deal cold damage become supernaturally cold, and the damage caused by these effects is not subject to being reduced by a creature's cold resistance. Creatures with cold immunity take half damage from such attacks. Truefrost elixir has no effect on cold damage from weapons, on non-cold-based effects, or against creatures without immunity to cold or cold resistance.<br><p><b>Base Item:</b> </p><h3><b>Requirements</b></h3><p>Craft Wondrous Item, polar midnightUM</p><h3><b>Source: </b></h3>AP 70",
